title: Week 8 Studs & Duds + Monday Punday, Blame Mike - Fantasy Football Podcast for 11/1
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, get a recap of the biggest Studs & Duds of Week 8! Which disappointing performances are the most concerning going forward? Plus, major injury updates and the Week 8 edition of Monday Punday! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for November 1st, 2021.
  
 (04:40) - Monday Punday
 (06:10) - NFL News

 (43:00) - Fantasy Duds
